lead_paragraph: Jordan Staal scored on a rebound in overtime, Eddie Lack stopped 31 shots and the Carolina Hurricanes downed the Toronto Maple Leafs 1-0 on Thursday night.

headline.main: Jordan Staal Scores in OT and Hurricanes Beat Leafs 1-0
